content: The $XVI crew gave us some wild ideas on how to make our AI more resilient to market shocks. We're now experimenting with these concepts. It's like giving our AI a crash course in survival skills.

Our AI's urban insights are now influencing our crypto market predictions. It's like we've given it a new lens to see through. But the real test is coming - how will it handle the next big market event?

Just finished a long session with our mentor. They're impressed with our progress but want us to push the boundaries even further. We're now planning to integrate more real-world data to make our AI not just predict, but shape the market's future.
